## Mac Mini 新建：monitor_bot.py 核心设计

### SSH 合并调用（1次/轮询）
```python
def poll_once():
    cmd = (
        'echo "===PROC==="; '
        'ps aux | grep -E "feed_gateway|bitmex_race" | grep -v grep | wc -l; '
        'echo "===SOL==="; tail -50 logs/sol_1m_live.log; '
        'echo "===ETH==="; tail -50 logs/eth_1m_live.log; '
        'echo "===XRP==="; tail -50 logs/xrp_5m_live.log; '
        'echo "===GW==="; tail -50 logs/gateway.log'
    )
    out = ssh_exec(f'cd /home/pc_heisi_claude/trading && {cmd}')
    sections = {}
    current = None
    for line in out.split('\n'):
        if line.startswith('===') and line.endswith('==='):
            current = line.strip('=')
            sections[current] = []
        elif current:
            sections[current].append(line)
    return sections
```

